{"tid":1025831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國社會學家：教會裡80％神父是同性戀","createTime":"2019-02-17T15:27:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T07:00:37.000Z","uid":28765,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cd5cb65dc2d244784417fb10b59eb72b7b1ee8ae","tid":1025831,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T15:27:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phphZ9CvQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phphZ9CvQ.jpg&h=c71de661&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法國社會學家的新書稱許多神職人員過著「兩面生活」，還稱教會裡5個神職人員中有4個就是同性戀。（美聯社 資料照）<br />\n<br />\n2019-02-17 16:59<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕法國社會學家、同性戀的馬特爾（Frederic Martel）的新書《梵諦岡的衣櫃裡（In the Closet of the Vatican）》，記述4年來暗訪超過1500名神職人員的調查，內容稱許多神職人員過著「兩面生活」，還稱教會裡5個神職人員中，有4個就是同性戀。<br />\n<br />\n據《法新社》報導，馬特爾稱梵諦岡內幾乎都是同性戀，過去50年來教會在道德立場上大多有解釋權，但事實上教會內部正在搖擺。馬特爾表示，教廷對於性議題的態度出現快速變化，大概是在1960到1970年代，教廷為了掩蓋內部的秘密，不得不表現出對同性戀的厭惡。「我已經開始了解如何引述教宗方濟各（Pope Francis），這個機構建立在謊言、兩面生活和虛偽之上。」<br />\n<br />\n馬特爾說，這種掩蓋事實的作風對教會帶來最大的副作用，正是接二連三動搖教會根基的性虐兒童事件，雖然性虐與同性戀毫無關聯，但因主教害怕媒體知道教會隱藏的秘密，也一併包庇了虐兒神父。<br />\n<br />\n據《CNN》報導，馬特爾的調查也引起爭議，由於新書於20日才正式發行，許多人關心「80%神職人員是同性戀」的依據為何？此外，馬特爾的調查方法較少使用傳統記者的方法，如錄音或文字文件，來源有待考證。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2701501\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2701501&d=MHEGAcVJLkfiWkVsZ9yRxk6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=39d2c6cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2701501&h=2cfaa527\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2701501</a>"},{"pid":"60169f9968b16d877e2cb7fdb5347fe72dffee6a","tid":1025831,"uid":199902,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T15:30:46.000Z","msg":"法國社會學家：教會裡100％神父孌童"},{"pid":"d151fded88a375c2d7c799be6229f8c6f67ce581","tid":1025831,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T16:17:23.000Z","msg":"神愛世人<br />\n咁神係咪BI？"},{"pid":"940a5877fb0f0fcd87482121fbcd0e86eb7a3377","tid":1025831,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T16:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1042d92df90644fab3f67fe959a0f12ff3414d01","tid":1025831,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T16:25:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0de9afaacd5c88ff0bee1ab1177134ca4c10ae8e","tid":1025831,"uid":169676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T17:24:59.000Z","msg":"係未古羅馬遺留落嚟嘅風氣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7b1f04e58d89c4b3bc5c54b623d6a65a9cde29","tid":1025831,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T17:33:21.000Z","msg":"可能無性戀"},{"pid":"a718caf4f7e284d0faacba5f93ceef080d466595","tid":1025831,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:04:40.000Z","msg":"方濟各後生時開發過幾多個男學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcdeb1c01597d449acb3aa4acd16a7608190daa3","tid":1025831,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:23:22.000Z","msg":"其實係咪因為聖經唔比近女色結果去咗另一個極端<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f4027546ce4fc3df1348ee30afbb30f7d50ce3","tid":1025831,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcdeb1c01597d449acb3aa4acd16a7608190daa3","tid":1025831,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:23:22.000Z","msg":"其實係咪因為聖經唔比近女色結果去咗另一個極端<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:57:04.000Z","msg":"其實聖經好似冇話唔畀 最初班神父係可以結婚<br />\n禁慾係之後嘅事"},